### ── PRICING SERVICE (/pricing) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

### 1. Get price history — Porsche 911 (has seed data in PriceHistory)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pricing/getPriceHistory(vehicleId='40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005')
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 2. List price history via entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/pricing/PriceHistory?$filter=vehicle_ID eq 40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. Update price — Admin, lower Golf VIII price
POST {{baseUrl}}/pricing/updatePrice
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001",
  "newPrice": 27500.00,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### 4. Price history after update — new record should be present
GET {{baseUrl}}/pricing/getPriceHistory(vehicleId='40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001')
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 5. Compare to list price — Audi A4
GET {{baseUrl}}/pricing/compareToListPrice(vehicleId='40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000004',offerAmount=35000)
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 6. Update price as Customer — should be rejected (Admin/Manager only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pricing/updatePrice
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001",
  "newPrice": 1.00,
  "currency": "EUR"
}
